snippet.title: Nova's Adventure SAGE 2024 - Demo
snippet.description:
This is a fun little demo I came across this year's SAGE
It reminds me of Bomb Kirby from KSS on the SNES

Note the game is in a very early state!

I am not one of the Devs!

This is not a SPEEDRUN!
(I just like going fast)

Support the devs and nab the demo here:
https://sonicfangameshq.com/forums/showcase/novas-adventure.2334/ 

I hope to see the full version of this game in the future!

Thanks for watching!
